# Repo-root build context (captain-definition / docker compose build from here).
# Keep secrets, local databases, and build junk out of the Docker build context.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/data/
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
web-service/docs/
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.claude
.vscode
printer-service/
README.md
